{
  "text": "Immunoblotting was performed as described [CITATION_1] . PGC1a antibody was a gift provided by Alan L Schwartz (65), originally generated in the laboratory of Daniel Kelly [CITATION_2] . Antibodies from Cell Signaling Technologies (Beverly MA) were: b-Actin (#4970); GAPDH (#5174). ALOXE3 (#ab118470) and UCP1 antisera (#ab155117) were from Abcam (Cambridge, MA). LC3B antiserum was obtained from Novus Biologicals (Littleton, CO) (#NB-100-2200).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "13239888",
